C.U.P.I.D.S. 001(2014)(Digital)(TLK-EMPIRE-HD) 


Welcome to C.U.P.I.D.S.: the Cherub Union for the Preservation of Intimacy, Devotion and Sensuality. Armed with chemically engineered crossbows, cloaks and superhuman skills, the C.U.P.I.D.S. have secretly controlled human romance for millennia. But their reign is about to be challenged, and human society will hang in the balance.
